On the latest episode of Hemmer Time, Bill sits down with the Host of “Justice With Judge Jeanine”, Jeanine Pirro, to talk about the death Gabby Petito and disappearance of her fiancé, Brian Laundrie.
Jeanine discusses why she thinks the Petito family did not report their daughter missing until ten days after her boyfriend returned home to Florida. She also details how she suspects Gabby was killed and whether she believes Brian currently is still alive.
